Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:35.46,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}It is currently the Great Age of Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.01,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}A struggle between countless pirates began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.59,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while looking for the great treasure, One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.18,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}left behind by the legendary Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:47.18,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}The boy who became a rubber man after eating the Gomu Gomu Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.10,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monkey D. Luffy, is one of the many adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.52,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}who went out to sea to become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.98,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Luffy and his companions have already experienced countless adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:03:00.82,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}Not even the World Government can ignore their existence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.66,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:07.24,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What adventure is waiting for us next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.79,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Today, the crew aiming for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:14.13,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}will continue through the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:21.01,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy has been separated from the Straw Hat Crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:25.72,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and is heading for Navy HQ to save his brother Ace, who is about to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:29.43,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the other Straw Hats are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.73,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We now go a little back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:47.01,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Unexpectedly, Zoro ended up stranded with Perona.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.78,Thoughts,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...  I gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:04.81,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that useless swordsman go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.67,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:25.58,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the room I was sleeping in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.83,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, a maze?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.98,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.60,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.89,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna entertain myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:05:00.18,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,by sending him into the depths of despair with my Negative Hollows as soon as he found his swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:02.78,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I even told him where the swords were...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.99,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,but he's just been running around for two whole days!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:11.76,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't he find them, even though I gave him clear directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:20.00,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing here?!\NAre you using your Devil Fruit powers again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:23.88,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!  Don't try to blame this on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.26,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,You're just LOST, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:32.92,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, if you go up one of the stairways behind us the room with your swords will be right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:35.51,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,How could you get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:38.58,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Shaddup!  Your directions were confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.23,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way this is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.99,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a fantasist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.65,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,It's right over THERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:48.03,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how could you get that wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:53.43,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,You've become a pitiful guy since I took your swords away, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:57.84,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at what you've become,\Nit feels like my heart's gonna break...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.46,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so sorry for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.30,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,What're you crying for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.55,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, something good will happen for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.51,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.47,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:19.22,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.44,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,What's your game here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.90,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing any games.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:29.37,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get your swords back, I'm a hollow, none of your attacks can hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.87,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,They just pass straight through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:35.25,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,A swordsman like yourself is no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:38.37,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I have no need for a servant who isn't cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:47.79,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd just give his swords back for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:51.42,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,If I use him, I can get back to Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.91,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,His head is so totally empty, I can manipulate him easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:07:01.44,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him work and work, and when I'm done I'll just leave him on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.36,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:13.41,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  He got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:17.45,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that useless swordsman go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.95,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Luffy and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.66,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta get back to the Sabaody Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.34,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.98,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,EVERYONE, JUST THINK OF HOW TO ESCAPE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.18,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,RIGHT NOW...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.14,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,WE CAN'T...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.48,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,BEAT THEM!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:54.53,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't waste any more time here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:07.50,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.97,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I've been here before, but maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:15.84,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.60,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I must have seen a similar castle before!  Now, that's confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.38,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it, you moron!  I can't believe how bad your sense of direction is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:32.19,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how nice I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.75,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually leading him to the coast...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.96,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.  I'll politely lead him there, then make him work like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.95,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it's this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:44.32,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!  Yes, I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:48.45,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Just follow my lead and don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.67,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.88,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  Why are you going off in a different direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.48,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Oh, is it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.88,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you it isn't, you stupid swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:00.62,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.86,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you even just follow me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.32,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to give better directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.91,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,How is this my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.49,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted just being around this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.24,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.01,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You're flying, but you're exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:23.78,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:24.83,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:28.50,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.  I get tired just from talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.91,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize this tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.68,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.22,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.75,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone else has come flying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.94,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.11,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:55.41,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of helping a boring, troublesome toy like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.66,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,You can just wander the island for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.87,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of person it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.18,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope it's a cute one this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.13,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  You sure took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.63,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Why are YOU here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:21.54,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you ask?  Wasn't the coast over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.93,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,So you really ARE a fantasist, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.87,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:31.44,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really an amazing guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.17,Thoughts,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,That tree...  The cuts are new...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:11:00.34,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so disappointed...  We only heard a tree falling over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.11,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was sent flying here after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.66,Thoughts,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I have to stick with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:12.13,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this battlefield-like atmosphere...  It feels like I'm gonna melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.79,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that tree was cut down by some lingering evil spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.99,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.24,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.49,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.50,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.04,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,A grave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.87,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.81,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a single piece cut from a large tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.05,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,This is an impressive piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:17.59,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it sure is big...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.79,Thoughts,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,There it is again...  Somebody's here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.44,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Fast...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.46,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  He deflected it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.71,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.28,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,These guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:39.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:47.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:51.94,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namakura Island, Kingdom of Poverty, Harahetternia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:56.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,It is here that the locals have mistaken Brook for the Demon King, Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.53,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,What a pleasant morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.66,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:21.54,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if all of you are looking at this sun as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.96,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am sure they are looking at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.51,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Because no matter how deep the night, it always turns to day eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:34.18,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're all alive, I am sure I will see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:49.11,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I must say...  this is a very run-down island...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:53.03,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,About that room...  I didn't notice it yesterday, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.87,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,there was a ceremonial altar and dolls that seemed to be made for worship,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.11,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,with strange tapestries and posters on the walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:03.29,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,and all those macabre-looking wall hangings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:07.80,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,And the things on the floor, were they cursed tools of some sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:12.71,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, it was all rather strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.97,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:21.65,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We gathered some breakfast for you, and we were just on our way to your room to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.65,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.73,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.52,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,What generous people you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering food for a stranger like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.95,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've forgotten to introduce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:39.58,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I am the head of this land, Pekkori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.46,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Pekkori-san.  I will accept your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.30,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:16:00.05,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:05.61,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,He wants panties!  Hurry and show him your panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:12.65,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!  You see...  I wasn't actually...  talking about the men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:16.53,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.49,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:25.63,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,That was such a good meal.  I am completely stuffed, and can barely move...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:31.34,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Though I do not have a stomach to stuff in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.61,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That was one week's worth of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.51,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,We've just gotta endure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:45.02,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Satan-sama?  What is it you want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.36,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to set out to sea as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.28,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give me a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:54.06,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!  Have we angered you somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.28,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:59.33,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all of you! Show him his after-meal panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.40,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the panti- WHOA!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.59,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Have you come to dislike panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.54,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,No...  That is not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:15.77,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get back to my companions, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:16.77,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.43,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.47,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.85,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.  I am sorry for causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.83,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:32.03,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,If the panties won't work, we have no means of stopping you, Satan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.67,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,This kingdom is done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:39.64,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this, we have no choice but to accept death together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.75,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.09,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:44.19,Main,Men,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.76,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there seems to be some complicated story behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:54.21,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,You all call me "Satan", and yesterday, I seem to recall hearing something about a "Longhand Tribe."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.89,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please tell me the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:08.20,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, this kingdom has been under siege from the Longhand Tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.86,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Not only do they take all of our money and food,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:15.77,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,but they also abduct our skilled men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.90,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, the kingdom is worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:21.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all suffering from poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.26,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the food you gave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:29.84,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ashamed to admit this, but we just scraped together what little food we had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:30.71,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:34.70,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,In an attempt to escape our desperate situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:40.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,we kept praying to one god after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:45.07,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,And not only that, we also called upon skilled spirit masters from nearby countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.94,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,in an attempt to curse and kill our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:53.99,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,However, that did not work either.  Since we'd run out of options, we resorted to black magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:59.92,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,and at last, succeeded in summoning you, Satan-sama, The Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:04.41,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Satan-sama, you are our last hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:07.79,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Please, bestow your judgment upon the Longhand Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:09.62,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,We beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.37,Main,Men,0000,0000,0000,,We beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.12,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:18.13,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!  We want you to cast your curse of death upon our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:21.34,Main,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Satan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.68,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.02,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Longhand Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:29.85,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.26,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.89,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to punch you, you damn bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.92,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Give that girl back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:49.13,Main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave us alone, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.21,Main,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,Give my daughter back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:54.51,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna send you all to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.34,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.89,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.55,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that woman is being taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.66,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.40,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Now, cast your curse upon them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.02,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.18,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,No, we have to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.76,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Satan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.12,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:30.80,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Still, even though that girl, their own comrade, was taken away, all they do is talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:34.62,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't they try to fight, to take her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:35.88,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Satan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.16,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,We beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:41.70,Main,Pekkori,0000,0000,0000,,Bestow upon them your divine judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.55,Main,Men,0000,0000,0000,,We beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:49.57,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,These people depend on others too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:56.72,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,But that young lady is the victim here!  She hasn't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:03.03,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.  I need to repay my debt for your hospitality and the panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:16.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan! Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.00,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san.  Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:24.63,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I am currently surrounded by an abundance of panties, while being hailed as "Satan-sama".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.37,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, but you will have to wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:31.24,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't repay a certain debt, I'll be just as useless as any other skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:37.21,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I have finished this job, I will head back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:52.52,Thoughts,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,It's been one hour since we left Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:57.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind keeps up, it wouldn't be a surprise if we arrived at Navy HQ very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:00.72,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we move any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:05.70,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not arrive after the battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:07.55,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.55,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy won't take down Whitebeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:12.62,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:14.31,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,You're still talking like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:17.90,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind taking your head first, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.19,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:48.16,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming now!  Wait for me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:13.16,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others continue their voyage on the Tarai Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:16.49,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Not much time remains before they reach Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:21.33,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy watches the Vivre Card to make sure that Ace is still safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:24.05,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,while he thinks back on his past with Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:25.38,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:28.06,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Flashback Special before Marineford
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:29.26,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The Brothers' Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:31.57,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
